          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿呀，你未能事人，焉能事鬼。"
        },
        {
          "character": "罗卜",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我父将终，"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘青提",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那都是迂谈。不要听他。"
        },
        {
          "character": "罗卜",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "休言我父多迂。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘青提",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿但知三年无改，岂不闻如其道，终身无改可也。如其非道，何待三年？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘青提",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你父敬浮屠。"
        },
        {
          "character": "罗卜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老娘。佛像在堂，休出此言。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘青提",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿呀，娘立心已定，说下断头话来。诸佛神像在上。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘青提",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "若要我吃斋把素似当初。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘青提",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不知母亲听信哪个谗言，改变心肠。是了。舅爷到此，一定是舅爷的言词。舅"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（黄莺儿） 为何劝娘开荤酒。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘青提",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你起来，劝娘休学郗后之言，如何解说？"
        },
        {
          "character": "罗卜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "昔日梁武帝皇后郗氏，不信神明，死后变为蟒蛇。武帝代为忏悔，方才得还人"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘青提",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "武帝既能度其妻，吾儿必能度其母。"
        },
        {
          "character": "罗卜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老娘还当见贤思齐，因何学不贤之辈？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘青提",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来我儿志不可。方才所言，亦非劝你开荤。你父亡过，恐你道心不定，特来"
        },
        {
          "character": "罗卜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此，多谢老娘。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘青提",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "还有一事，母子商量。"
        },
        {
          "character": "罗卜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有何事情？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘青提",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只今济僧布施，费用浩大。你可出外做些买卖，生些利息。则前功可继，后用"
        },
        {
          "character": "罗卜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "禀告老娘。孩儿幼依膝下，不惯经商，怎生去得？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘青提",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你若去，我着益利作伴，料也无妨。"
        },
        {
          "character": "罗卜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孩儿舍不得老娘。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘青提",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我今生幸未衰，你正当勇往向前不可达拗。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（益利上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "益利",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "佛殿烧香犹未毕，高堂有唤又忙来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "益利",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "禀安人有何使命？"
        },
        {
          "character": "益利",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "因为时年不丰，求济甚多，唯恐后不应前，令与东人远行贸易，觅些利来，已"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（黄莺儿） 这生财有道方能久。"
        },
        {
          "character": "益利",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老安人年老在堂，小官人经营不惯。伏望思忖，莫遣远行。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘青提",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我立心已定谁敢违。"
        },
        {
          "character": "罗卜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "益利，安人发怒，少不得顺从前去。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（益利允。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "罗卜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "焚起香来。待我辞别神圣。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（泣颜回） 辞圣离故里，"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘青提",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "思忆何事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "罗卜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孩儿、益利在家，僧济贫，照例实行。孩儿、益利远去他乡，犹恐违却父志，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（泣颜回） 愿老娘遵守着一念慈悲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "罗卜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老娘忧虑何来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘青提",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我儿孝心如是，去到他乡，必然牵挂老娘。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（泣颜回） 怕你在途中早晚有谁调理，"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘青提",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小官人年幼，自幼未曾远行。你是年长之人，能知异乡风景，此去逢船过渡，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（泣颜回） 在旅店安歇，迟行早宿，"
        },
        {
          "character": "益利",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "半担行李受驱驰。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘青提",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好生服侍东人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "益利",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奉东人自当协力。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（尾声） 匆匆拜别登程去，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（罗卜、刘青提同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘青提",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "金奴，我见小官人去得可怜，是我心中疼痛起来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "金奴",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有益利相伴，安人放心。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘青提、金奴同下。）"
        }
      ],
