    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第二场",
      "characters_present": [
        "益利",
        "罗卜"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（罗卜上，益利随上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夏日苦炎热，早行须趁凉。"
        },
        {
          "character": "益利",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "竹清风渐爽，荷放露生香。"
        },
        {
          "character": "罗卜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "益利。"
        },
        {
          "character": "益利",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小官人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "罗卜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我奉母亲严命，往外经营。身虽离了家门，心则常在膝下。思念不已，如何是"
        },
        {
          "character": "益利",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呵小官人。你我奉老安人之命，此去贸易，觅利便归。身在途中，休要嗟叹。"
        },
        {
          "character": "罗卜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "言之有理。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（新水令） 绿荫冉冉路漫漫。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（驻马听） 椿树摧残，椿树摧残。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（得胜令） 伤情对景有千般。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（罗卜、益利同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（完）"
        }
      ],
